snippet.title: Flying Soldiers - Launch Date Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Get ready to command an odd squad of fun birds and devise a plan to bring them safe and sound to the end of the battlefield. An outlandish puzzle game that will challenge your mind to make these greenhorn recruits into brave soldiers.
